{"root":{"data":{"id":"dhr36rl2z2o0","created":1775987955823,"text":"Resilient Manufacturing-韧性制造","font-weight":"bold"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhr384v2cv40","created":1775988063089,"text":"概念和重要性","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhr3fypnqcg0","created":1775988676614,"text":"Resilience 系统在扰动后恢复稳定的动态能力\nResiliency 系统表现韧性的静态状态属性"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhr3h0fo6hs0","created":1775988758728,"text":"Resilient Manufacturing 系统在运行过程中保持业务连续性的能力 ","layout_right_offset":{"x":21,"y":0},"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhr4f49csew0","created":1775991431435,"text":"静态韧性-无中断，维持运行稳定性"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhr4f7ar4540","created":1775991438050,"text":"动态韧性-中断下，感知预测学习适应的循环过程"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhr4gpakcxc0","created":1775991555585,"text":"三大驱动力：社会经济驱动，技术创新驱动，环境保护驱动"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhr389osij40","created":1775988073593,"text":"识别扰动","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhr4r86mw280","created":1775992380348,"text":"扰动-通过制造不连续性、混乱或失序来中断或阻碍正常运营的事件"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhr4s5qd5z40","created":1775992453374,"text":"外部扰动：自然灾害，疫情"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhr4sceimv40","created":1775992467896,"text":"内部扰动：设备故障，技术失误"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhr4slulh600","created":1775992488459,"text":"五级分类框架&预防与响应策略"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhr4spjcmog0","created":1775992496486,"text":"机器级"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhr4vvtan7c0","created":1775992745240,"text":"预测性维护"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhr4ssfmvxs0","created":1775992502792,"text":"操作级"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhr4vyujmio0","created":1775992751846,"text":"协同计划"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhr4suboi7k0","created":1775992506906,"text":"企业级"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhr4svwob7k0","created":1775992510352,"text":"市场与社会级"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhr4v67h6a00","created":1775992689502,"text":"扰动的演化模式"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhr4veovt080","created":1775992707968,"text":"正常"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhr4vh